name: Blyat Jump
description:
Getting the seed of your level:

Press K to get the seed

Double Click  

CTRL A and CTRL C copies the entire text box

To submit levels you have made to be added to the main levels selection, use https://forms.gle/WGQKpkN8DQCCZAVT7 to access said form.

For Base Project https://editor.p5js.org/BlyatBoio/full/ERBS_pK_D

Entire game made in the P5JS Web Editor

Feedback more than welcome, would love to know what to improve!
